  "features": [
    "Safe Material & Hollow Design:Featuring a charming and playful design, this baby teething toy is perfect for capturing your little one's attention and keeping them entertained. Adopting scientific hollow structure design, the annular hole precisely fits the grasping curve of babies. Crafted from 100% food-grade silicone, it's soft, free of sharp edges, and provides a safe, soothing chewing experience for your baby. It has passed the U.S. CPSIA, ASTM F963, EU EN71, and CE safety standards.",
    "Soothe Teething Discomfort:The teether chew toy can be refrigerated for use, featured multiple raised textures gently massage your baby's gums, effectively relieving teething discomfort. The chewing action also helps strengthen oral muscles, promoting healthy development for speech skills. This toddler teether does not only soothe baby to sleep, also help children with autism, ADHD, or sensory processing needs, to reduce irritability and ease emotions.",
    "Easy to Clean :One-piece molded food-grade silicone teething toy with the design of honeycomb holes, which can accelerate drainage water evaporation. Finally, simply air dry or hang to dry for optimal hygiene and can be safely sterilized using UV light, boiling water, or a steam cleaner.With no small parts to eliminate choking hazards, its durable design is built to withstand daily wear and tear.",
    "Enhances Both Physical & Cognitive Development:Soft and perfectly sized, This teether toy is safe for babies aged 3 6 12 and 18 months to use, with no risk of scratching or choking. Its soft material encourage fine motor skill development as babies press, squeeze, and explore. The different raised texture also stimulate tactile and visual coordination, promoting brain development. Suitable for babies aged 0 to 24 months, it's a versatile tool for early learning and growth.",
    "Compact & Travel-Friendly:This teething has a hollowed out design that makes it easy to carry around, parents can attach it with a lanyard or store it in a small rucksack or pouch at any time, making it the perfect travel companion—whether you're on a plane, train, or in the car. It also makes a wonderful gift for birthdays, baby showers, Christmas, Thanksgiving, New Year's, Children's Day, Easter, or any special occasion. Give the gift of comfort and joy with this adorable silicone teether!"
  ],
  "description": "Product Description Why to Choose Our Teething Toys? -Teething usually causes mouth discomfort, such as sore gums, so the baby may be more likely to bite and cry. Adorable bunny shape teething toys for any babies who are chewing and gnawing to help those teeth break through sore gums! -Hollow Design, Adopting scientific hollow structure design, the annular hole precisely fits the grasping curve of babies. Crafted from food-grade silicone, it's soft, free of sharp edges, and provides a safe, soothing chewing experience for your baby. -Easy to carry &amp; clean, One-piece molded food-grade silicone teething toy with the design of honeycomb holes, which can accelerate drainage water evaporation. Parents can attach it with a lanyard or store it in a small rucksack or pouch at any time, making it the perfect travel companion—whether you're on a plane, train, or in the car. -Develop baby’s multiple ability: Color recognition ability, shape cognition ability, grip ability, hand-eye coordination ability and oral development. -It makes a wonderful gift for birthdays, baby showers, Christmas, Thanksgiving, New Year's, Children's Day, Easter, or any special occasion. Give the gift of comfort and joy with this adorable silicone teether!",
